snippet.title: Red Tree Crime
snippet.description: Being a True Crime lover myself, I wanted to share stories of some of the worst crimes to have taken place. I hope to not only educate people but also to entertain them as well. I also wanted to create this channel as a way for other True Crime lovers to meet and discuss crime and criminals. When I was younger, I took several college courses on Human Psychology and have family members who are police officers. Thank you so much for checking us out.
